    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Japanese Leptobatopsis spp., males (A, B) and females (C–F)—A, B: head and mesosoma, dorsal view; C, D: T II, dorso-lateral view; E, F: wings, dorsal view. A, C: L. annularis Kasparyan, 2007; B, D, F: L. nigricapitis Chandra & Gupta, 1977; E: L. appendiculata Momoi, 1960." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8309330/files/figure.png" ;
